'''羊皮'''是一種取自羊身上的皮革。不像其它一般的[[皮革|皮革]]，羊皮通常都會保留皮上的[[羊毛|羊毛]]。

== 用途 ==
羊皮通常都會用于製作鞋，帽和坐墊。在[[澳洲|澳洲]]和[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]，羊皮是[[Ugg靴|Ugg靴]]的主要原材料。<ref>[http://ozwool.net/numnah.html Dressage & General Purpose Numnahs] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090124231937/http://ozwool.net/numnah.html |date=2009-01-24 }} Retrieved on 2 February 2009</ref> <ref>[http://www.threebagsfull.com.au/sheepskin_products.htm Sheepskin Products] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081120122224/http://www.threebagsfull.com.au/sheepskin_products.htm |date=2008-11-20 }}  Retrieved on 2 February 2009</ref>

